>              0              0              0             82            562
>  seq2:501-1000 seq2:1001-1500 seq2:1501-1584
>            709              0              0
>> sapply(scanBam(bf, param=param), FUN)
>     seq1:1-500  seq1:501-1000 seq1:1001-1500 seq1:1501-1575     seq2:1-500
>              0              0              0              0              0
